## Telegram UX Examples

**You say:** `"Hey, market looks choppy today, be careful"`

**Agent 0 replies:**
```
🎖️ COMMANDER BRIEFING — Strategic Review Initiated

📊 Agent 6 (Macro): Market regime = CHOPPY. BTC down 4%, Fear index high.
⚖️ Agent 7 (Risk): 2/5 trades today resulted in losses. Daily loss at 40% of limit.

🧠 My Reading:
I recommend reducing position sizes to 5% (from 10%) and raising the Agent 5 
threshold from 8.0 → 8.5 to filter out marginal signals.

[This is a DEFENSIVE action — applying automatically in 5 minutes]
```

**You say:** `"I want to go aggressive, raise the position sizes"`

**Agent 0 replies:**
```
🎖️ COMMANDER PROPOSAL — Needs Your Approval

📊 Agent 6 (Macro): Market regime = BULLISH. SOL up 8% week.
⚖️ Agent 7 (Risk): No daily losses yet. Kill Switch at Tier 0 (clear).

🧠 My Reading:
Raising position size from 10% → 15% of capital. This would increase max 
position exposure from $1.50 to $2.25 on current $15 capital.

⚠️ Risk: This amplifies both gains AND losses. In a 5-trade losing session, 
daily loss limit would be hit faster.

Reply /approve abc123 to confirm, or /reject abc123 to cancel.
━━━━━━━━
Proposal ID: abc123 | Expires: 30 minutes
```

